Prometheus exporter for hardware and OS metrics exposed by *NIX kernels,
written in Go with pluggable metric collectors.

WWW: https://github.com/prometheus/node_exporter

***Please note that this needs to be enabled via Services: Prometheus Exporter.

The source for this plugin is located at https://github.com/opnsense/plugins/edit/master/sysutils/node_exporter

Changelog
---------

1.2

* Allow setting IPv6 addresses as ListenAddress

1.1

* Allow to toggle the "zfs" collector
* Fixed disabling collectors:
    cpu
    exec
    filesystem
    loadavg
    meminfo
    netdev
    time

1.0

* Node exporter server
* Allow to toggle collectors:
    cpu
    exec
    filesystem
    loadavg
    meminfo
    netdev
    ntp
    time
    devstat
